Span.Text: "Our innovative use of technology and integration of Microsoft products into our fleet provides the personal service our customers expect and helps ensure they make it to their most important commitments."
Joanne Smith, SVP, in Flight Services, Delta Air Lines
Microsoft Dynamics for Retail mobile point-of-sale is enabling Delta Airlines to provide personal service to 160 million+ customers annually.

Windows 10 tablets reduce the weight required for paper flight books on-board, and provide the pilot with a highly secure connection to corporate resources, all in one enterprise-class device. With modern EFB applications, pilots employ a single device for planning, filing, and flying: collaborating with air traffic control from the cockpit, signing pre-flight plans remotely, marking plans naturally in the cabin, and filing them upon arrival with the tap of a button.
Collaboration and corporate communications are easily accomplished from the same device, whether swapping shifts with other pilots, consuming training, or simply checking and responding to email.
Boost the productivity of your in-flight crew
Lower the weight, lower the cost
